name: The items in the Sort dropdown should be visible when clicking on the Sort dropdown button
The text in the Search field should match the input text after typing in the Search field
The item names on the main page should contain the text from the Search field after performing a search
The search field should have a placeholder when loading the Home page
The search field should be empty after clicking on the Search Reset button
The count of items on the main page should match the expected count and item names after searching for a specific term
The "Home Page" title should be visible on the Home page
The item price values should be between the selected min and max price set on the Price Range slider
